# Feature Requirements for CoinAtlasApp

## Market Screen
- Display trading rankings with percentage changes
- Show market cards for currency pairs with:
  - Buy/sell rates
  - Percentage change
  - Interactive chart visualization
  - News summary affecting the pair
- Implement card hover/touch effects
- Support "time travel" animation when refreshing data

## Signals Screen
- Create immersive sentiment visualization for assets
- Display sentiment cards with:
  - Asset name (Bitcoin, Gold, etc.)
  - Sentiment mood indicator
  - Trend direction
  - Interactive chart with glow effects
- Support particle effects for visual enhancement
- Enable zooming to see macro/micro views of sentiment

## Insights Screen
- Implement timeline-based news feed
- Display news events with:
  - Time indicator (e.g., "2 hours ago")
  - Event title
  - Summary description
  - Visual indicators for impact level
- Support highlighting related market effects
- Enable smooth scrolling with animation effects

## Settings Screen
- Organize settings in card-based categories
- Include items with:
  - Colored icons
  - Clear labels
  - Chevron indicators for navigation
  - Proper grouping of related items
- Required settings sections:
  - Support (FAQ, Tutorials)
  - Legal (User Agreement, Privacy)
  - App Information (Version, About)

## Navigation
- Implement tab-based navigation with smooth transitions
- Update active tab indicator based on scroll position
- Support gesture-based navigation between screens
